No. 11-5565. Nina Shahin, Petitioner v. Delaware, et al. 565 U.S. 807, 132 S. Ct. 387,

181 L. Ed. 2d 8,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6356. October 3, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari *9to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
